{"tid":2329950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支付寶好先進？ 人民銀行：任何單位及個人不得拒收人民幣現金","createTime":"2020-12-17T15:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T16:03:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f3fc7d4b51c6ee4585222f008b0f9d02378b62","tid":2329950,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:06:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200930/bkn-20200930153308215-0930_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200930%2Fbkn-20200930153308215-0930_00842_001.html&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28R9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=08ff9d02\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200930/bkn-20200930153308215-0930_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行官方社交平台發文稱，人民幣是中國的法定貨幣，任何單位和個人不得拒收人民幣現金。<br />\n<br />\n人行表示，一貫鼓勵現金、非現金等多元化支付方式和諧發展，並採取多項措施，保障公眾安全、乾淨使用現金，籲各收付主體尊重公眾的支付選擇權，共同維護人民幣的法定地位。"},{"pid":"1c6e8fc05f8dc9cc49bfb57c0d113862caf2e32a","tid":2329950,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"支付狗 PR 去晒邊？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0725923a49c336327a646b83ae7fe3a3fffe8e4c","tid":2329950,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55ef9e7cfe575be119af6d85132c9cd5c08e7f5","tid":2329950,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0725923a49c336327a646b83ae7fe3a3fffe8e4c","tid":2329950,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"BITCOIN啦"}]}